    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> hake fillet[s]</strong> to a plate and season all over with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>cornflour </strong>all over and rub it into both sides of the fish until fully coated</p><p>Tip: Coat the fish in the cornflour one side at a time to avoid stickiness!</p>",
